{"id":"df035165-4769-4de0-8844-a4f8bedaa1b3","name":"IJN Yamato, Musashi, Shinano | Your Floofy Haven","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Description: </strong>Welcome home, Commander. The mighty Yamato-class of the Sakura Empire are awaiting your return. Yamato, the eldest and most disciplined of the sisters, stands ready alongside the second sister, Musashi. And Shinano, the class's sole aircraft carrier, completes this trio of fox-eared shipgirls, all eager to greet you after your long mission.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Series: </strong>Azur Lane</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Note: </strong>IJN<strong> </strong>Yamato version here is an unofficial/fanmade interpretation based on Dishwasher1910's OC concept art of her. Musashi and Shinano are based on their current official versions in Azur Lane.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 612px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2a3606ad-a6a4-445a-a8d5-de0dbb524ed5_c820bb1a-d772-475e-93f8-d4e54e288bd6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 612px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2a3606ad-a6a4-445a-a8d5-de0dbb524ed5_174f1ca9-9676-40d8-88eb-22d54e0133f5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 614px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2a3606ad-a6a4-445a-a8d5-de0dbb524ed5_9762a559-d51c-40f1-a51a-f215622eb2d3.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 617px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2a3606ad-a6a4-445a-a8d5-de0dbb524ed5_d662b285-9547-4cb5-b54b-94bf617b1c1f.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>All of my Yamato-class bots:</strong></p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.c